platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Be a vet and heal the animals

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Fox and Sheeps endearing app gives kids the power to healand helps parents encourage kindness and curiosity. Through trial and error, little ones figure out how to treat a sniffly owl, a sunburned rabbit, and other beautifully animated patients. Sometimes they need bandages and medicine; sometimes a healthy snack will do the trick. Animals flashbacks and reactions offer important clues in the delightful quest to make them smile again.
